dy": [{"kind": "text", "text": ", aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (T, M, Msb, K,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^adarN", "text_ar": "اَدَرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Lth, T, S, Mgh) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^adarapN", "text_ar": "اَدَرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Lth, TA,) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^udorapN", "text_ar": "اُدْرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (as in the TT,) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^udorapN", "text_ar": "اُدْرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is a simple subst., (M, K,) and so is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^udorapN", "text_ar": "اُدْرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a man, S)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "had the disorder termed"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^udorapN", "text_ar": "اُدْرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (T, S, M, &c.)"}], "source_refs": ["T", "M", "Msb", "K", "Lth", "S", "Mgh", "TA"]}, {"entry_id": "n12320", "headword_ar": "ادرّ", "root": "dr", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He made"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "milk"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to flow,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to flow copiously,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "abundantly:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he drew forth"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "milk. (Msb.) See also 1, in three places. ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^adar~uwA AlxaraAja", "text_ar": "اَدَرُّوا الخَرَاجَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(the collectors)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "made the produce of the tax called"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "xrAj", "text_ar": "خراج"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to come in abundantly."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) ―         -b3-  [And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Adr~ Albawola", "text_ar": "ادرّ البَوْلَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a medicine, &c.,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "caused the urine to flow plentifully; acted as a diuretic;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(see the act. part. n. below;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Astdrhu", "text_ar": "استدرهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".] ―         -b4-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Adr~ A^um~ahu", "text_ar": "ادرّ اُمَّهُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a young camel)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sucked,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "drew the milk of, his mother."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Adr~hA", "text_ar": "ادرّها"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He stroked her"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a camel's)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "dugs, to draw her milk: he milked her;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AstdrhA", "text_ar": "استدرها", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", referring to a ewe or she-goat: (Msb: and the latter,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he stroked her dugs with his hand, causing the milk to flow,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to flow copiously:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and the same verb,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he sought,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "desired, her milk,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the flowing of her milk."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) ―         -b5-  [Hence,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^adiruwA liqoHapa A@lmusolimiyna", "text_ar": "اَدِرُوا لِقْحَةَ ا@لمُسْلِمِينَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Make ye. the tribute, or taxes, pertaining to the Muslims to pour in abundantly:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "lit.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "make ye the milchcamel of the Muslims to yield milk abundantly"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: said by 'Omar to the collector of the taxes. (TA.) ―         -b6-  [Hence, also,] one says to a man, when he seeks a thing, and begs for it importunately,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^adir~ahaA wa A_ino A^abato", "text_ar": "اَدِرَّهَا وَ اـِنْ اَبَتْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning, [lit.,]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Ply her, though she refuse, until she yield her milk abundantly."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) ―         -b7-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^adar~a A@ll~`hu lahu A^axolaAfa Alr~izoqi", "text_ar": "اَدَرَّ ا@للّٰهُ لَهُ اَخْلَافَ الرِّزْقِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "God milked for him the dugs of sustenance;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "provided for him the means of subsistence"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "niEomapa A@ll~`hi biAl$~ukori", "text_ar": "نِعْمَةَ ا@للّٰهِ بِالشُّكْرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Astd~r", "text_ar": "استدّر", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He drew the favour, or blessing, of God, by thankfulness"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A.) ―         -b8-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Alr~iyHu tudir~u Als~aHaAba", "text_ar": "الرِّيحُ تُدِرُّ السَّحَابَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, L, K,) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tasotadir~uhu", "text_ar": "تَسْتَدِرُّهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, L,) (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The wind draws forth a shower of fine rain from the clouds:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, L, K: in some copies of the last, we find, as the explanation of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^adar~ati Alr~iyHu Als~aHaAba", "text_ar": "اَدَرَّتِ الرِّيحُ السَّحَابَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", instead of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Halabatohu", "text_ar": "حَلَبَتْهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", [agreeably with the above explanation,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jalabatohu", "text_ar": "جَلَبَتْهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "j", "text_ar": "ج"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": the explanation in the [S and] L is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tasotaHolibuhu", "text_ar": "تَسْتَحْلِبُهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": TA:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Als~aHaAba", "text_ar": "السَّحَابَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nasotadir~u", "text_ar": "نَسْتَدِرُّ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "We desire, or look for, a shower of rain from the clouds"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hlb", "text_ar": "حلب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) ―         -b9-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bayona Eayonayohi", "text_ar": "بَيْنَ عَيْنَيْهِ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EiroqN yudir~uhu AlgaDabu", "text_ar": "عِرْقٌ يُدِرُّهُ الغَضَبُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(said in a trad., TA) (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Between his eyes was a vein which anger caused to flow;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S; *) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to fill with blood;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A;) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to become thick and full:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "which anger put in motion:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S:) for (TA)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^adar~a Al$~aYo'a", "text_ar": "اَدَرَّ الشَّىْءَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he put the thing in motion."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, TA.) ―         -b10-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Adr~t Almigozala", "text_ar": "ادرّت المِغْزَلَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "She twisted the spindle vehemently,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "so that it seemed to be still in consequence of its vehement twirling."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, * TA.) ―         -b11-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Adr~ Als~ahoma", "text_ar": "ادرّ السَّهْمَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He made the arrow to turn round well upon the nail"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(AHn, K *)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of his left thumb, turning it with the thumb and fore finger of his right hand."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(AHn. [See 1, latter part.]) ―         -b12-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^adorarotu Ealayohi", "text_ar": "اَدْرَرْتُ عَلَيْهِ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlD~arobu", "text_ar": "الضَّرْبُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I inflicted upon him an uninterrupted beating."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A.)"}], "source_refs": ["S", "L", "K", "TA", "A"]}]}, "classical_definitions": {"source": "hawramani", "url": "https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%A3%D8%AF%D8%B1/", "headword_ar": "أدر", "entries": [{"lexicon_id": "dictionary_12", "lexicon_en": "Al-Muṭarrizī, al-Mughrib fī Tartīb al-Muʿrib (d. 1213 CE)", "lexicon_ar": "المغرب في ترتيب المعرب للمُطَرِّزي", "permalink": "https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=91#82e4ac", "body_html": "(أ د ر) : (الْأَدَرُ) وَهُوَ مَصْدَرٌ الْآدَرُ وَهُوَ الْأَنْفَخُ بِهِ أُدْرَةٌ وَهِيَ عِظَمُ الْخُصَى."}, {"lexicon_id": "dictionary_36", "lexicon_en": "Al-Ṣāḥib bin ʿAbbād, Al-Muḥīṭ fī l-Lugha (d. c. 995 CE)", "lexicon_ar": "المحيط في اللغة للصاحب بن عباد", "permalink": "https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=91#bb00bc", "body_html": "<span class=\"title1\">أدر</span><br>الأدَرُ: المُنْتَفِخُ الخُصْيَتَيْنِ، والفِعْلُ أدِرَ يَأدَر أدَراً، وهي الأدْرَةُ والأدَرَةُ. والمَادِيْرُ: هُمُ الأدْرُ، والقِيَاسُ مِئْدَارٌ."}, {"lexicon_id": "dictionary_21", "lexicon_en": "Muḥammad al-Fattinī, Majmaʿ Biḥār al-Anwār fī Gharāʾib al-Tanzīl wa Laṭāʾif al-Akhbār (d. 1578 CE)", "lexicon_ar": "مجمع بحار الأنوار للفَتِّنيّ", "permalink": "https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=91#c16714", "body_html": "<span class=\"title1\">[أدر]</span><span> نه فيه: فذهبت عنه \"الأدرة\" بالضم نفخة في الخصية رجل أدر بين الأدر بفتح الهمزة والدال. ومنه: قولهم أن موسى أدر بهمزة ممدودة فدال مهملة مفتوحة فراء مخففة.</span>"}, {"lexicon_id": "dictionary_6", "lexicon_en": "Ismāʿīl bin Ḥammād al-Jawharī, Tāj al-Lugha wa Ṣiḥāḥ al-ʿArabīya (d. 1003 CE)", "lexicon_ar": "تاج اللغة وصِحاح العربية للجوهري", "permalink": "https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=91#f16445", "body_html": "<span class=\"title1\">[أدر]</span><span> الأُدْرَةُ: نفَخةٌ في الخصية. يقال: رجل آدَرُ بيِّن الأُدْرَةِ.</span><span> </span><a></a><a></a>"}, {"lexicon_id": "dictionary_8", "lexicon_en": "Ibn Sīda al-Mursī, Al-Muḥkam wa-l-Muḥīṭ al-Aʿẓam (d. 1066 CE)", "lexicon_ar": "المحكم والمحيط الأعظم لابن سيده الأندلسي", "permalink": "https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=91#6c5e24", "body_html": "<span>[أد ر] الآدَرُ والَمأْدُورُ: الذَّيِ يَنْفَتِقُ صِفاقُه، فَيقَعُ قُصْبُه، ولا يَنْفَتِقُ إلا من جانِبِه الأَيْسَر، وقيلَ: هو الَّذِي يُصِيبُه فَتْقٌ في إِحْدَى الخُصْيَتَيْنِ. ولا يُقالُ: امْرَأَةُ أَدْرَاءُ، إمّا لأَنَّه لم يُسْمَعْ، وإِمّا أَنْ يكونَ لاخْتِلافِ الخِلْقَةِ. وَقَدْ أَدِرَ أَدَراً، والاسمُ الأُدْرَةُ. وقيلَ: الخُصْيَةُ الأَدْراءُ: العَظِيمَةُ من غيرِ فَتْقٍ.</span>"}, {"lexicon_id": "dictionary_10", "lexicon_en": "Abū Mūsā al-Madīnī, al-Majmūʿ al-Mughīth fī Gharībay al-Qurʾān wa-l-Ḥadīth (d. 1185 CE)", "lexicon_ar": "المجموع المغيث في غريبي القرآن والحديث لأبو موسى المديني", "permalink": "https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=91#d016d6", "body_html": "<span class=\"title1\">(أدر)</span><span> - في الحديث: \"أَنَّ رجلا أَتاه وبه أُدرَةٌ فقال: ائتِ بعُسًّ فحَسَا منه. ثم مَجَّه فيه، وقال انتَضِحْ به فدهَبَت عنه\".</span><br><span>قال الأصمعى: الأَدَرُ والأدَرَة، والأُدْرَة: أن تَضخُم الخُصْيَة من فَتْق أو غَيْره، قِيلَ: كان صِبْيان يَلعَبُون ويَنْزُون فَنَهاهم ناهٍ، فقال أعرابى: دعهم يَأْدَرُوا.</span><span> </span><span>- وفي الحديث: \"أَنَّ بَنِى إسْرائِيل كانوا يقولون: إنَّ مُوسَى آدَرُ\".</span><br><span>من أَجْلِ أنَّه كان لا يَغْتَسِل إلا وَحدَه. وفيه أُنزِل قَولُه تَعالَى: {لَا تَكُونُوا كَالَّذِينَ آذَوْا مُوسَى </span><span class=\"red\">...</span><span>} الآية.</span><br><span>والفِعْلُ أَدِرَ يَأْدَر .</span>"}, {"lexicon_id": "dictionary_1", "lexicon_en": "Ibn Manẓūr, Lisān al-ʿArab (d. 1311 CE)", "lexicon_ar": "لسان العرب لابن منظور", "permalink": "https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=91#7c5a27", "body_html": "<p>أدر: الأُدْرَةُ، بالضم: نفخةٌ في الخُصْيةِ؛ يقال: رجل آدَرُ بَيْنُ</p><p>الأَدَرِ. غيرُه: الأَدَرُ والمأْدُورُ الذي يَنْفَتِقُ صِفاقُهُ فيَقعُ</p><p>قُصْبُه ولا يَنْفَتِقُ إِلاَّ من جانبه الأَيسرِ، وقيل: هو الذي يُصيبهُ</p><p>فَتْقٌ في إِحدى الخُصْيتينِ، ولا يقال امرأَةٌ أَدْراءُ، إِما لأَنه لم</p><p>يُسْمَعْ، وإِما أَن يكون لاختلاف الخِلْقَة؛ وقد أَدِرَ يأْدَرُ أَدَراً،</p><p>فهو آدَرُ، والاسم الأُدْرَةُ؛ وقيل: الأدَرَةُ الخُصْيَةُ، والخُصْيَةُ</p><p>الأَدْراءُ: العظيمةُ من غير فَتْقٍ. وفي الحديث: أَنَّ رجلاً أَتاه وبه</p><p>أُدْرَةٌ، فقال: ائْتِ بِعُسٍّ، فحَسا مَجَّه فيه، وقال: انْتَضِحْ به،</p><p>فذهبت عنه الأُدْرَةُ. ورجل آدَرُ: بَيْنُ الأَدَرَةِ، بفتح الهمزة</p><p>والدال، وهي التي تسميها الناسُ القَيْلَةَ. ومنه الحديث: إِن بني إِسرائيلَ</p><p>كانوا يقولونَ إِن موسى آدَرُ، من أَجل أَنه كان لا يغتَسل إِلاَّ وحدَه.</p><p>وفيه نزل قوله تعالى: ولا تكونوا كالذين آذَوْا موسى (الآية). الليث:</p><p>الأَدَرَةُ والأَدَرُ مصدران، والأُدْرَةُ اسم تلك المنْتَفِخَة، والآدَرُ</p><p>نَعْتٌ.</p>"}, {"lexicon_id": "dictionary_32", "lexicon_en": "Supplément aux dictionnaires arabes by Reinhart Dozy (d. 1883 CE)", "lexicon_ar": "تكملة المعاجم العربية لرينهارت دوزي", "permalink": "https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=91#cf5d1d", "body_html": "أدر: آدر: وقد كتبت في معجم فوك أدر وفيه جمعها: أدار."}]}, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}